  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to minicom</title>

    <para>
      The <application>minicom</application> package provides a serial
      communication program. It is provided in this chapter for communicating
      with UNIX 3.51 on <xref linkend="freebee"/> and transferring files over
      <computeroutput>xmodem</computeroutput>.
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&minicom-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

